                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The only record that has been found of this meeting, aside from the entry in the
                    Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_660">p. 660</ref>, is the
                    reference to it which appears in a telegram of December 12, 1943, from the
                    Ambassador to the Greek Government-in-Exile in Egypt (<persName corresp="#p_ML1"
                        >MacVeagh</persName>) to the Secretary of State, <hi rend="italic"
                    >post</hi>, <ref target="#pg_844">p. 844</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
